k-600 transition-colors\">Kontakt</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"hidden lg:flex\">\n          <a href=\"#objednat\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-pink-500 to-orange-400 px-4 py-2 text-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-pink-400/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all\">\n            Objednat\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">🍓</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div id=\"navDrawer\" class=\"lg:hidden mt-3 hidden\">\n        <div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white/90 shadow ring-1 ring-white/60 glass p-4\">\n          <ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n            <li><a href=\"#produkty\" class=\"block rounded-xl px-3 py-2 hover:bg-slate-100\">Produkty</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#rodice\" class=\"block rounded-xl px-3 py-2 hover:bg-slate-100\">Pro rodiče</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#mise\" class=\"block rounded-xl px-3 py-2 hover:bg-slate-100\">Naše mise</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#kontakt\" class=\"block rounded-xl px-3 py-2 hover:bg-slate-100\">Kontakt</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#objednat\" class=\"mt-2 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-pink-500 to-orange-400 px-4 py-2 text-white shadow-lg\">Objednat 🍓</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </nav>\n  </header>\n\n  <!-- Hero -->\n  <section class=\"relative z-10\">\n    <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 sm:py-16\">\n      <div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center\">\n        <div>\n          <span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-lime-200 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 ring-1 ring-lime-300\">\n            Novinka! <span class=\"text-pink-600\">Svačiny bez přidaného cukru</span>\n          </span>\n          <h1 class=\"mt-4 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-slate-900\">\n            Zdravé svačiny pro děti<br class=\"hidden sm:block\" />\n            